Under the MOU the DOE and the six manufacturers will collaborate to gather and exchange information relating to five major areas : research and development related to turbine reliability and operability ; siting strategies for wind power facilities ; standards development for turbine certification and universal interconnection of wind turbines ; manufacturing advances in design process automation and fabrication techniques ; and workforce development .
